First Read: 26-Feb-26
HB514 Enrolled
1 Enrolled, An Act,
2
3 Relating to Tuscaloosa County; to further provide for
4 the compensation of the sheriff.
5 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
6 Section 1. (a) Beginning June 1, 2026, the Sheriff of
7 Tuscaloosa County shall receive an additional expense
8 allowance of thirty-six thousand dollars ($36,000) per year,
9 payable in equal monthly installments from the county general
10 fund. This expense allowance shall be in addition to all other
11 expense allowances or other forms of compensation and shall be
12 treated as compensation for retirement contributions.
13 (b) This subsection shall be void upon the next vacancy
14 in the Office of the Sheriff of Tuscaloosa County.
15 Section 2. This act shall become effective on June 1,
16 2026.
